d hourly rate places them above the upper quartile.     Hickman Industries’ workforce consists of 83.17% males and 16.83% females.  The figures set out above have been calculated using the snapshot date of 5th April 2017 and the standard methodologies used in the Equality Act 2010 (Gender Pay Gap Information).                         Our ETFS Division Just Gets Better and Better!    Substantial investment in our Engineered Timber Floor System (ETFS) Division means there are even more reasons for buying your I-Beam floor systems from National Hickman.    Read More        Investment brings real improvements for customers and suppliers alike!    We have great news – since National Hickman joined Masonite, an investment programme in IT infrastructure and computer operating systems for both the Door Kit and Fibercill product ranges has been on-going.    Read More        Masonite acquires Hickman Industries Ltd    One of the world’s leading door manufacturers, Masonite International Corporation, has bought Hickman Industries Limited, a manufacturing company specialising in customised product solutions supplied into the new build market, including MDF architectural mouldings, doorkits, and engineered timber floor systems.    Read More                      Our Latest News  Sent to your inbox    Email *                  This iframe contains the logic required to handle AJAX powered Gravity Forms.      Follow us on  All of our favourite social media ...        Facebook    Twitter    Vimeo    RSS       © 2009 - 2018 National Hickman - Established - 1892 | Privacy Policy | Human Rights  Website by Cloud 9       Welcome, our website uses cookies to improve your experience. We'll assume you're ok with this, but you can opt-out if you wish. Read More  Accept & Hide this message                               